      "title": "10-hr water cut for Colombo 5 & 6",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The National Water Supply and Drainage Board said that the water supply will be interrupted for 10 hours from 11 PM on Saturday (20) to 9 AM on Sunday (21) in Colombo 05 and 06.",
        "It added that a Low pressure supply will be experienced in Colombo 04."
      ],
